OL,3,CTop Gear needs a 'rethink' before
OL,4,Creturning to TV former presenter
OL,5,CJames May says
OL,7,FFormer Top Gear presenter James May
OL,8,Fhas said it would be a "shame" if the
OL,9,FBBC does not give Top Gear a
OL,10,F"rethink".
OL,12,FThe 60-year-old, who used to present
OL,13,Fthe long-running motoring show with
OL,14,FJeremy Clarkson and Richard Hammond,
OL,15,Fspoke after the corporation said the
OL,16,Fhit series will be off air for the
OL,17,F"foreseeable future".
OL,19,FMay told BBC Radio 4's Today
OL,20,Fprogramme the decision is "very sad".
